<br />
Hence, France has an idiot in office that still thinks all violence is wrong even though they aren't really satisified with him.  Not to say they're on our side.  Most of them are too busy shopping for berets and practicing surrending techniques to give much of a damn about the Iraqi situation.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
